title: Bend Over
lastfmSummary: Kicked the door down and a man was in there and he went to get us, so I picked up a chair and threw it at him and started doing him in, nutted him and everything. We got out of there and we thought we'd go and have a bit of a spend-up and I bought some new boots and braces and some Levi stay-press.
